{"tid":1921370,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)湯漢屍系列","createTime":"2020-03-12T03:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T19:19:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff6ace65f8de041881e65d4811f4855d66d57c2","tid":1921370,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=b3f791c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=25c8dc5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=48f3c7c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a7/Cast_away_film_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa7%2FCast_away_film_poster.jpg&h=d59eb60a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://blog.xuite.net/ww41700/hkblog/140857998/cover600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.xuite.net%2Fww41700%2Fhkblog%2F140857998%2Fcover600.jpg&h=ac8c893d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9b/The_da_vinci_code.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9b%2FThe_da_vinci_code.jpg&h=16ef5619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1995年，聯邦快遞工程師查克乘坐公司飛機飛向馬來西亞，由於天氣原因飛機在南太平洋失事墜海，同機其他人員都遇了難，查克依靠救生氣囊幸運地活了下來，並漂移到了一個無人小島上。在島上他學會下水捕魚、鑽木取火等生存技巧。後來還見到了同機遇難的飛行員遺體，查克將對方的鞋子和手電筒取了下來為己所用，並將對方用土掩埋。為了生存，他還將公司所託運的幾個包裹打開，裡面各裝有威爾森牌排球、溜冰鞋和錄影帶等物品。他將溜冰鞋底面當作刀子使用，而在排球上畫了一張臉並取名為「威爾森」<br />\n<br />\n2.描述諾曼第登陸後，雷恩家4名於前線參戰的兒子中，3個兒子皆已於兩週內於海外各戰區陸續陣亡，其母親將在一天內接到三個兒子的死訊。而隸屬101空降師二等兵的小兒子詹姆斯&middot;法蘭西斯&middot;雷恩則在參與諾曼地的空降行動後下落不明，美國陸軍參謀長馬歇爾上將得知此事後出於人道考量，特令在法國前線作戰的美國陸軍遊騎兵組織一支8人小隊深入敵後，只為在人海茫茫、槍林彈雨中找出生死未卜的二等兵雷恩，並將其平安送回後方<br />\n<br />\n3.電影由羅浮宮館長雅克&middot;索尼埃（Jacques Sauniere）在館內被一名身穿修道服的持槍男子賽拉斯（Silas）追殺展開，塞拉斯逼問索尼埃拱心石（Priory's clef de voute，或Keystone）的下落，索尼埃與其他三位「守護者」一樣在臨死前撒了同樣的謊，說拱心石在巴黎聖蘇比教堂（Church of Saint-Sulpice）里的羅斯經線（Rose Line）下，塞拉斯信以為真，開槍射中索尼埃的腹部之後離開。與此同時，美國宗教符號學教授羅伯特&middot;蘭登（Robert Langdon，湯姆&middot;漢克斯飾）作為客座講師正在巴黎進行一場關於符號學和女性崇拜（sacred feminine）的演講。法國警方找到了他並將其帶到羅浮宮的案發現場<br />\n<br />\n4.在神父西爾瓦諾&middot;班提佛立歐和科學家維多利亞&middot;威特拉的注視下，歐洲核子研究組織（CERN）啟動大型強子對撞機，並捕捉到三小瓶反物質。過了不久，有人殺死西爾瓦諾，挖去了他的眼球，並用此眼球開啟了放置反物質的密室，進而取走其中一小瓶反物質，而西爾瓦諾的胸膛還被烙上一個神祕的印記<br />\n<br />\n5.哈佛大學教授勞勃&middot;蘭登（湯姆&middot;漢克斯 飾）在義大利佛羅倫斯一家醫院中醒來，他失去了過去幾天前的記憶，還被地球烤焦的鏡像困擾。席耶娜&middot;布魯克醫生（費莉絲蒂&middot;瓊斯 飾）告訴他，一枚子彈穿過他的大腦，造成失憶。隨後，刺客瓦任莎（安娜&middot;烏拉魯）偽裝成警察欲刺殺蘭登，她在通往蘭登病房的過道殺了一位醫生。慌亂中，席耶娜帶著蘭登逃進她的寓所<br />\n<br />\n12 25PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=5626dccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=e01fa676\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f5d7691f7a530a2ab64822427f1e09e399ab5f","tid":1921370,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60b5694c8f50a220f45ace050bc1b33d3c16b77","tid":1921370,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea65e7059506ad57b24ac6ef082b8ee39a41264","tid":1921370,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b1f418b55d517c752d6999e461f33fb02bf06e","tid":1921370,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41a7aa2b1e90f99cc4f0e2f361cf0bcbd91fa41","tid":1921370,"uid":29160,"like":0,"disl